{"questionId":"f196343a-4470-4649-8efb-edf349dd4393_11","correctAnswer":"B","section":"Math","steps":[{"title":"Solve the equation","content":"From $|x-8|=11$: $x-8=11$ or $x-8=-11$, so $x=19$ or $x=-3$."},{"title":"Sum the solutions","content":"Add: $19+(-3)=16$.<br/><br/>The answer is <strong>B</strong>."}]}